text.text:
What are Binary Options?
They are simple, quick and profitable!

(Part 1)

Binary Options (BO) are a simple, quick and beneficial way to earn money

text: in financial markets. They are likely to be the most profitable method to earn.

to get a large predetermined profit by trading binary options the only thing for you to do is to define exactly whether the chosen asset price (currency, oil, gold, Facebook) will increase or decrease within a given period of time.

The primary thing to know about Binary Options is to remember that you will get the whole profit in any case even if a dollar goes up by one cent!

Except for the simplest type of BO ‚Äì ‚Äúhigh/low‚Äù presented in our example, there are other types of binary options which allow getting even a greater profit.

text.text: Don‚Äôt you know anything about currency movements, and don‚Äôt you want to trade currency in Binary Options?!

text.text:
What are Binary Options?
They are simple, quick and profitable!

text:
Minimal Risk and Guaranteed IncomeThe essence of Binary Option trading consists in the correct estimation of asset profitability within a definite period of time.
If your supposition comes true, you will make money. Otherwise you will lose your money.
However, the size of both losses and profit is known in advance. Taking a decision on buying or selling an option a trader knows exactly how much money can be lost or earned.
This is one of the key differences of Binary Options from other trading types where losses can considerably exceed the asset cost.

Depending on circumstances each successful transaction brings a trader not less than 65% of its sum. In many cases this level is even higher, up to 91%.

‚Äì This classic binary option is ideal for novices in trading. All you have to know is to determine where the asset price will go: up or down.
If the asset price changes by one point or more in your direction by the option expiration, you will get profit.
The income of BO transactions can be 100% of funds invested. Forecast the price trend to buy an option ‚ÄúHigh‚Äù or ‚ÄúLow‚Äù.

‚Äì Use the option, if you forecast the asset price to be within a given range.
If the asset price occurs within the given range by the option expiration, the transaction income can be 100% of funds invested.
Make your predictions and buy ‚ÄúRange‚Äù option.

‚Äì The profit can be obtained with binary options if the asset price has touched some given levels.
Your transaction income can be up to 90% if the asset price has touched the definite boundaries at least once.
It can be both upper or lower levels. Forecast the price trend and buy options ‚ÄúTouch Up‚Äù or ‚ÄúTouch Down‚Äù.

text.text:
What are Binary Options?
They are simple, quick and profitable!
After looking through sites we have found some of the best binary options strategies for trading our tricky pseudo-financial instrument. We will present our comments on their secrets in turn:

text:
They call it ‚ÄúDouble up‚Äù and say that if you consider an asset to go in the direction you have opened the position in, you should double your investment.
Firstly, taking psychology into account a person who is already losing is inclined to double, secondly we have heard that this strategy causes the greatest losses; it is true especially for those who don‚Äôt follow strict discipline and don‚Äôt have any definite experience.

text.text: (But aren‚Äôt you that kind of a person?!)

text:
Binary options have their contract expiry time (60 secs, 30 min, 1h, 1 week, etc.), this function allows traders who are losing money to transfer their positions to the following expiry time.
In principle, it is the same Martingale, why? The thing is when you transfer your position to the next time your investment grows by 30%.
The situation is:

text.text: you are losing money, and you are given some hope to get back all your investment if you add no less than 30%

text: . (Can‚Äôt you use that?!) Such a function (strategy) works only once.

At first sight they seem to be basic, but in fact, they have nothing to do with common options, because they have been originally invented to get profit.
Most of the sites recommend this binary options strategy for you at least to reduce your potential losses

text.text: (in case the price goes against you, take the opposite direction)

text:
, there is some risk of losing both in Put and Call, if the price is in between contracts by the expiry time.
The confusion appears due to the fact that a new instrument is very simplified, that is ‚ÄúPut‚Äù means ‚Äúdown‚Äù and ‚ÄúCall‚Äù means ‚Äúup‚Äù, with no variations to sell options.

text.text:
What are Binary Options?
They are simple, quick and profitable!
The temptation to earn 80% of your investment in some minutes is more connected with gambling than a reasonable approach to trading.

text: It is important to understand that to trade such types of options means that you use your working capital minding the reasonable distribution of risks.

The possibilities to react adequately while working on the so called noises within short time periods are minimal.
If you consider binary options as an income source but not a roulette game, we advise you to start with buying long-term options.
Well, you won‚Äôt get profit immediately, it will take hours, but you will have much more chances to win, which means your profit will grow and let you improve your skills.

text.text: How to Choose a Proper Broker and Get Profit?
Of course, to get profit is of primary importance for anyone who starts trading binary options.

text: But how to choose the best binary options broker who will pay you back the earned profit in time?

text.text: Not all the companies can boast by their good reputations in this respect, so try to observe the following rules:

text:
1. Be very careful choosing brokers and check their reputations.
2. Don‚Äôt open an account using a borrowed name, it can complicate the payout.
3. Be careful reading all the rules of working with a broker.
4. Check the terms of bonus offers.

text.text: Which Information Do You Have to Check?
To choose a broker you have to check the following information:

text:
1. Who provides the given broker with quotes?
2. The possibility of opening a demo-account?
3. Providing the training facilities and materials?
4. The availability of customer support services?

text.text:
What are Binary Options?
They are simple, quick and profitable!
Trading operations are simple but not from the viewpoint of psychology.

text:
The problem is to take decisions which do not always seem to be logical; the optimal action is taken when it is separated from your emotions.
As the result will directly depend on your emotional state, you have to stop trading while being emotionally unstable and do your best to relax.
Don‚Äôt let your emotions overcome You and get You to deviate from the chosen strategy.

text.text: Is it Real to Get Profit?
Any trading in financial markets requires some basic skills.

text:
As a rule, novices greatly lack discipline. In principle, the absence of discipline is the main reason of losing at the stock exchange.
Simple though it might sound, but 90% of traders do lose their deposits due to the lack of that discipline.
So it is crucial to be ambitious, ready to learn and admit your mistakes, only in this case your success will not be long in coming.

The statement that it is impossible to earn on binary options is principally wrong. Really, trading is not a simple deal, and it doesn‚Äôt come easily to everybody.
Perhaps, you will never earn for a private penthouse in Miami-Beach, and a new Ferrari will never appear in your garage.
By the way, the same can be said about any other market, the only puzzle is where these successful traders come from.
All of them seem to be permanent lucky dogs.

text.text: Why Are Binary Options Are Getting More and More Popular

Let‚Äôs delve a little bit deeper and find out why are binary options are getting more and more popular.

1. Traders incur Minimal risks
If you compare binary options to other financial trading instruments, you quickly realize how much of a lower risk it is.

text:
For example, traders can start with as little as $1, which is quite favorable for someone who‚Äôs just starting out and still inexperienced. Moreover, you can also predict how much you are going to win or lose.

It allows traders to choose to invest just the specific amounts which they are willing to part with; there are never issues of shocks and surprises. The best thing is that the platform allows you to continue betting with small amounts regardless of how experienced you are.

Although the returns are way smaller when you opt for lower investments, you can be confident that the amount you are willing to risk does not affect your entire financial situation.

text.text: 2. Simple and Secure Handling of Assets
It‚Äôs a straightforward type of trading option which anyone, including novices who have no skill in CFD trading.

text:
For instance, it‚Äôs designed with structures, and functions which make it easy for each and every trader. All you need to do is choose a reputable broker and deposit the amount you feel can fetch the best ROI. secure

Again, you just need to know whether your underlying asset is going upwards or downwards, for you to place a bet.
So you need to be alert and make the right prediction based on the price movement of the type of asset you choose to trade in.
You can also rely on a few software to help you make the right predictions.

Not much effort is required from there on, apart from having to sit back and track your trade. Another thing with this type of trade execution is that it‚Äôs so much easier to learn and adapt.

For instance, you can increase your chances of winning by keenly studying the past price performance of some of the popular assets.
Previous price patterns and trends can help you to make the right predictions.

text:
‚ö†Ô∏è  Martingale in Binary Option? Should or not?

üìå What is martingale strategy?

 Double your previous losses until you finally win, resulting in profits no matter what, as long as you can go far. The only limiting factor is the size of your account, so as long as you can make your next trade you will have a 50/50 chance of earning all your money back.

 ‚úÖ  Advantages: 

- high profitability when the market is in flat
- work at any volatility ‚Äì and when the market is relatively active and trendy, and when the movement is minimal

 ‚ùå  Disadvantages

- periodically lead to a complete loss of deposit with recoilless trends;
- when working with martingale, strong nerves are required, which not all traders have.

text:
‚ö°Ô∏è‚ö°Ô∏è‚ö°Ô∏è Any binary options trading platform gives you the opportunity to make a lot of money, but it will also be a place to "burn" a lot of money if investors do not have a proper and reasonable trading strategy.
Here are some basic capital management strategies that investors should keep in their mind.

‚õ≥Ô∏è   Quantify risky capital 
To put it simply, out of the total amount of money you have, determine a limited amount that you are "willing to lose" in order to trade. This is called the reasonable risk capital that each investor should limit himself to.

‚ùå  Do not trade too fast
Remember, trade with an amount less than your own risk capital limit, and be very careful when placing transactions for the required length of time.
üè∑  Look at the reality 
You must accept risks and losses when trading and you must take measures to be ready to face the financial risk of your investments before you can reap huge returns from them. 

üî± Always Be Prepared For The Worst
We don't know exactly whether tomorrow's price will go up or down - but we have a lot of evidence of past price movements. Looking closely at past price chain signals is one of the most effective ways to make predictions about future prices.

üîñ Have a long-term route
Having a long-term route in using capital, new investors can calculate exactly how to allocate capital from time to time to maximize the financial efficiency of the money source. This is the core factor that determines the long-term success or failure of a binary options investor.

text.text: WHAT IS BUY/SELL OPTION? WHAT IS THE DIFFERENCE?

text: ‚úÖ

a buy option gives the buyer the right to buy an underlying asset at a designated price (the strike price) for a specified period of time. In return, the buyer of the right has to immediately pay the right seller an amount of money called the option fee, the right seller is obliged to sell the property when the buyer takes the right ( to buy the property).

‚úÖ

: a sell option gives the buyer the right to sell an underlying asset at a designated price (the strike price) to the seller of the put option. In return, the right buyer has to pay the seller a fee. The seller of the right is obliged to buy the property when the buyer exercises the right ( to sell the property).

üëâüëâüëâ
